data.title: The Whistler
data.meta_description: The Whistler is a series of films produced by Larry Darmour Productions during the 1940s. It was adapted from the radio show of the same name. Recently, we've done several changes to help out this wiki, from deleting empty pages, improving the navigation, adding a rules page, as well as merging film infoboxes.
